You've spoken and we have heard you, people of Sea Peue!

You asked for Independence and freedom from your benevolent rulers in OpenITC Vale so we've decided to include what every VPS provider in the industry is lacking instead. An album of free music which we'll release an uninstall tool for next week!*

Our DireVPS have roots in the the lifelong influences of Linus Torvalds and Richard Stallman. It's a collection of code and scripts made possible only by shared time and life experiences.

At DireVPS, music has never been a big part of who we are and what we do nor is it the solution our customers need but the solution it deserves.


